---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About" description="Discover the Pomodoro technique and how our app helps you maximize productivity with deep focus sessions.">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-16">
    
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="text-center space-y-6 py-8">
      <div class="text-6xl mb-4">üçÖ</div>
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-extrabold bg-gradient-to-r from-primary via-secondary to-accent bg-clip-text text-transparent">
        The Pomodoro Technique
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-base-content/80 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A simple yet powerful method to improve your focus and productivity
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- What is Pomodoro -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">What is the Pomodoro Technique?</h2>
      <div class="card bg-base-200 shadow-xl">
        <div class="card-body">
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            The Pomodoro Technique was created by <span class="font-bold text-primary">Francesco Cirillo</span> in the late 1980s. 
            The name comes from the tomato-shaped kitchen timer (pomodoro in Italian) he used during university.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
            This technique breaks work into <span class="badge badge-primary">25-minute</span> intervals called "pomodoros", 
            separated by short breaks. It's perfect for fighting procrastination and maintaining focus.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- How it Works -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">How Does it Work?</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">
        
        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/10 to-primary/5 border border-primary/20">
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="badge badge-primary badge-lg">1</div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Choose a task</h3>
            </div>
            <p>Select the task you want to work on. It can be anything: studying, coding, writing, designing...</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary/10 to-secondary/5 border border-secondary/20">
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="badge badge-secondary badge-lg">2</div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Work for 25 minutes</h3>
            </div>
            <p>Focus completely on your task for 25 minutes. No distractions, no social media, no multitasking.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-accent/5 border border-accent/20">
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="badge badge-accent badge-lg">3</div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Take a 5-minute break</h3>
            </div>
            <p>Take a short break. Stand up, stretch, drink water. Let your mind relax.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-gradient-to-br from-info/10 to-info/5 border border-info/20">
          <div class="card-body">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <div class="badge badge-info badge-lg">4</div>
              <h3 class="card-title text-xl">Repeat and long break</h3>
            </div>
            <p>After 4 pomodoros, take a longer break of 15-30 minutes. You've earned it!</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- App Features -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">App Features</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
        
        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">‚è±Ô∏è</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Smart Timer</h3>
            <p>Automatically alternates between work and rest. Set your available time and start.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üîî</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Notifications</h3>
            <p>Get sound alerts when each session ends. Never lose your rhythm.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üé®</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Customizable Themes</h3>
            <p>Light or dark mode. Choose the one that best suits your work environment.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üåê</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Multilingual</h3>
            <p>Available in Spanish and English. Switch languages anytime.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">üì±</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Responsive</h3>
            <p>Works perfectly on mobile, tablet, and desktop. Take your productivity everywhere.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card bg-base-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow">
          <div class="card-body items-center text-center">
            <div class="text-4xl mb-3">‚ö°</div>
            <h3 class="card-title">Fast & Lightweight</h3>
            <p>No installation, no registration. Open and start working immediately.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Benefits -->
    <section class="space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center">Benefits of Using Pomodoro</h2>
      <div class="grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
        
        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-2xl">‚úÖ</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Improves concentration</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">Short intervals help you maintain focus without mental exhaustion.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-2xl">‚úÖ</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Reduces procrastination</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">25 minutes is a manageable commitment. It's easier to start when you know it's temporary.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-2xl">‚úÖ</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Prevents burnout</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">Regular breaks prevent exhaustion and keep your energy high.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4 items-start p-4 bg-base-200 rounded-lg">
          <div class="text-2xl">‚úÖ</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-lg mb-1">Increases productivity</h3>
            <p class="text-base-content/80">Working in short sprints makes you more efficient and time-aware.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="text-center space-y-6 py-8">
      <div class="card bg-gradient-to-r from-primary/20 via-secondary/20 to-accent/20 border border-primary/30">
        <div class="card-body">
          <h2 class="card-title text-3xl justify-center mb-4">Ready to be more productive?</h2>
          <p class="text-lg mb-6">Start your first Pomodoro now and experience the difference</p>
          <div class="card-actions justify-center">
            <a href="/en" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
              Start Now
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7l5 5m0 0l-5 5m5-5H6" />
              </svg>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
